quote {
  id: number,
  title: !string,
  page: number,
  line: number,
  author: !string,
  genre: string, (romance, scifi, prose, non-fiction, poetry, etc.)
  type: string, (inspiration, motivation, prose, poetry, etc.)
  content: !string,
  user: id,
  claps: number,
  flags: number,
  hidden: boolean,
  comments: array,
}

user {
  id: number,
  name: string,
  collections: object,
}

collection {
  id: number,
  userId: number,
  quotes: array,
}

comment {
  id: number,
  content: string,
  quoteId: number,
  userId: number,
  claps: number,
  flags: number,
  hidden: boolean,
}


Special Functions
1. Duplicate checkers
2. Sort by (popularity, word match, etc.)


MVP
1. Quotes displaying all meta-data
2. Add quotes
3. Comment (add, edit, delete -- if userId is same)
4. Clap
5. Report
6. User accounts

FUTURE FEATURES (in order)
1. Sharing quotes on social media
2. Social media logins
3. Search and filtering options
4. Save quotes to personal collections
5. Other special functions (see above)
6. Ads and/or affiliate marketing
